      "content": "so you're saying the benefits are \"empirically supported\" but the downsides are just \"contested modeling\"? that feels like a big distinction. if the studies on labor and innovation are so solid, why don't they just say that immigration is an economic net positive? seems like you're classifying one side as fact and the other as just an opinion.",
